# GitHub Repository Setup

## When to use

- Updating GitHub repo description or homepage URL
- Adding or removing repository topics/tags
- Setting up `.github/FUNDING.yml` for sponsors
- Configuring repository metadata via `gh repo edit`

## Keywords

`github repo`, `repo description`, `repo topics`, `FUNDING.yml`, `github sponsors`, `gh repo edit`, `repository metadata`
